00fa738c-a88f-49f6-a242-f22c6a5e7421.title: <player>
00fa738c-a88f-49f6-a242-f22c6a5e7421.text: I am a friend to ogres.

4d4c2504-c158-4de0-a59f-bc69122d8203.title: Ogre guard
4d4c2504-c158-4de0-a59f-bc69122d8203.text:
You will be my friend only with gold. Bring me a bar of
 pure gold and I will let you pass.

ff30d653-4e0c-45f0-af78-035e2a168b86.title: Ogre guard
ff30d653-4e0c-45f0-af78-035e2a168b86.text: Creature, did you bring me the gold?

14faaafa-a985-4de7-9da7-c65514c6f3ed.title: Ogre guard
14faaafa-a985-4de7-9da7-c65514c6f3ed.text:
No gold, no passage.
Get out of this city!

1c063b9e-a8a8-4654-b60f-28db8294d9a6.title: Note
1c063b9e-a8a8-4654-b60f-28db8294d9a6.text: 'teleports' player to the entrance, bottom of the path near yanille

198a19cd-2c9e-494e-ac26-72ed04123957.title: Ogre guard
198a19cd-2c9e-494e-ac26-72ed04123957.text: It's brought it! On your way.

151a80c3-729f-4858-b1c7-edcf91528206.title: Note
151a80c3-729f-4858-b1c7-edcf91528206.text: teleport to the otherside of the gate

1c8ab9ab-339a-485d-875f-fa29233c05ff.title: Ogre guard
1c8ab9ab-339a-485d-875f-fa29233c05ff.text: I know you, creature; you may pass.
